quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  3,52,"Kwathi lapho uJesu esebona ukungakholwa ngasohlangothini lwabo wathi, “ngobani abazoba ngabasizi bami endleleni kaMvelinqangi na?” Abalandeli bathi thina singabasizi baMvelinqangi siyakholwa kuMvelinqangi futhi siyafakaza ukuthi singabazithobileyo ngaphansi kwentando yakhe"
  3,53,Nkosi yethu sikholelwa kulokho okwembulile futhi salandela isithunywa ngakho-ke sibhale phansi kanye nalabo abafakazayo
  3,54,Futhi babopha uzungu (abangakholwa) noMvelinqangi wabopha uzungu futhi uMvelinqangi ungcono (ngaphezulu) kwababopha uzungu
  3,55,"Futhi (khumbula) ngesikhathi uMvelinqangi ethi, “Oh Jesu! Ngizokuthatha ngikukhuphulele kumina ngizokuhlanza kulabo abangakholwa futhi ngenze labo abakulandelayo babe ngaphezulu kwalabo abangakholwa kuze kube usuku lokuvuka kwabafileyo, ngakho-ke niyobuyela kumina futhi ngiyokwahlulela phakathi kwenu kulokho enaniphikisana ngakho”"
  3,56,Ngakho-ke labo abangakholwa ngizobajezisa ngesijeziso esinzima kulomhlaba nasempilweni ezayo futhi angeke babe nabasizi
  3,57,Futhi labo abakholwayo futhi abenza izenzo ezinhle uzobakhokhela ngokugcwele umvuzo wabo futhi uMvelinqangi akazithandi izoni
  3,58,Yilokhu esinifundela kona emavesini nasesikhumbuzweni esiwubuhlakani
  3,59,Ngempela ukufana kuka-Jesu kuMvelinqangi kuyefana nalokho kuka-Adam wamdala ngothuli wayesethi kuyena iba (khona) wayeseba khona
  3,60,(Leli) yiqiniso elivela eNkosini yakho ngakho-ke ungabi (ngomunye) wabalabo abangabazayo
  3,61,"Noma ngabe ubani ophikisana nawe ngakho emva kokuba ulwazi selufikile kuwena ngakho-ke ithi, “Asibize amadodana ethu namadodana enu nabesifazane bethu nabesifazane benu nathi kanye nani bese siyazimisela emthandazweni sikhulekele isiqalekiso sikaMvelinqangi kulabo abaqamba amanga”"
  3,62,"Ngempela lena yindaba eyiqiniso, futhi akunanto enokukhonzwa ngaphandle kukaMvelinqangi ngempela uMvelinqangi ungophakeme ngamandlaonobuhlakani"
  3,63,Kepha uma befulathela ngempela uMvelinqangi uyazi ngezoni
  3,64,"Ithi, “Oh Bantu bencwadi! Sondelani ezwini elifanayo phakathi kwethu nani ukuthi angeke sibe nento enokukhonzwa ngaphandle kukaMvelinqangi nokuthi angeke senze abahlanganyele kanye naye nokuthi abanye bethu angeke bathathe abanye njengamakhosi esikhundleni sikaMvelinqangi” kepha uma befulathela ithi, “fakazani ukuthi singabazinikeleyo ngaphansi kwentando kaMvelinqangi”"
  3,65,Oh Bantu bencwadi! Kungani niphikisane ngo-Abrahamu kulapho iTorah neVangeli kwakungakambulwa kwaze kwambulwa emva kwakhe na? Ngakube aninawo umqondo na
  3,66,"Ngakube nina niyilabo abaphikisana ngalokho enaninolwazi ngako, kungan niphikisana ngalokho eningenalo ulwazi ngako na? Futhi uMvelinqangi uyazi kepha nina anazi"
  3,67,"U-Abrahamu wayengesiyena umJuda noma umKhrestu kodwa wayekholwe ngokweqiniso, ezinikele ngaphansi kwentando kaMvelinqangi futhi wayengesiyena omunye wabakhonza izithixo"
  3,68,Ngempela abaseduze kakhulu no-Abrahamu yilabo abamlandela yena kanye nalomphrofethi kanye nalabo abakholwayo. Futhi uMvelinqangi ungumngane walabo abakholwayo
  3,69,Iqembu labantu bencwadi lifisa ukuthi linidukise kepha abadukisi muntu ngaphandle kwemiphefumulo yabo kepha ababoni
  3,70,Oh Bantu bencwadi! Kungani ningakholelwa emavesini kaMvelinqangi nibe nifakaza (ngobuqiniso bawo)
  3,71,Oh Bantu bencwadi! (amaJuda namaKhrestu) kungani nimboza iqiniso ngamanga futhi nifihla iqiniso nibe nilazi
  3,72,"Futhi ingxenye yabantu bencwadi ithi, “kholelwani kulokho okwembulwa kulabo abakholwayo ekuqaleni kosuku futhi nikuphike ngasekugcineni kwalo mhlawumbe bangaphendukela (eqinisweni)”"
  3,73,"Futhi ningathembi (umuntu) ngaphandle kwalabo abalandela inkolo yenu ithi ngempela ukuholwa (ngokuyikho) ukuholwa nguMvelinqangi (ngakube) anikholwa ukuthi omunye engemukela okufanayo nenakwemukela noma baphikisane nani ngaphambili kweNkosi yenu, ithi ngempela umusa usesandleni sikaMvelinqangi uwunikeza lowo amthandayo futhi uMvelinqangi ungamele konke uyazi"
  3,74,Uyamkhetha ngomusa wakhe lowo amthandayo futhi uMvelinqangi ungumnini womusa omkhulu